Package ca.team4308.absolutelib.path

Interface OnTheFlyPathing.PathFactory<P,W,C,G>

Type Parameters:
P - Path type produced by the library
W - Waypoint type used by the library
C - Constraints/config type used during path construction
G - Goal/end-state type used to encode final heading or holonomic state
Enclosing class:
OnTheFlyPathing
public static interface OnTheFlyPathing.PathFactory<P,W,C,G>
Factory interface that adapts a concrete path library.
